<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Imam Hossain</title><link>/</link><description>Imam Hossain</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Mar 2021 01:13:03 +0600</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Get All Unique Timezone In Rails</title><link>/posts/first-post-get-unique-timezone/</link><pubDate>Thu, 18 Mar 2021 01:13:03 +0600</pubDate><guid>/posts/first-post-get-unique-timezone/</guid><description>&lt;h3 id="rails-timezone">Rails Timezone&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>There is only 35 Unique TimeZone worldwide ( According to Rails Timezone Class ). We can get a list of all the unique time happening worldwide by running the following snippet from rails console and see it ourselves. :smile:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby">
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">ActiveSupport&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">::&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">TimeZone&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>all&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>map(&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">:name&lt;/span>)&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>map &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">do&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">|&lt;/span>zone&lt;span style="color:#f92672">|&lt;/span>
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">Time&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>now&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>in_time_zone(zone)&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>strftime(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;%F %T %:z&amp;#39;&lt;/span>) }&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>uniq
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">end&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>To get the full list of 150 timezones&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4">&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby">
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">ActiveSupport&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">::&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">TimeZone&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>all&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>map(&lt;span style="color:#f92672">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">:name&lt;/span>)&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>map &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">do&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">|&lt;/span>zone&lt;span style="color:#f92672">|&lt;/span>
zone &lt;span style="color:#f92672">+&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39; : &amp;#39;&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#f92672">+&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">Time&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>now&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>in_time_zone(zone)&lt;span style="color:#f92672">.&lt;/span>strftime(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#39;%F %T %:z&amp;#39;&lt;/span>) }
&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">end&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>Thank you for reading!&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>